urdu transliteration text:
HAYE US BAALI SAKINA KO, KAHA NEEND AYEHJIS NE BABA KA GHALA AANKO SE KAT THA DHEKHA
@HujjatELC
AFTER SHE SAW HER FATHER’S HEAD BEING SEVERED

Youn to paani ko hai bechayn pyaasey kitnayhumney pysaaso ko tarastey huvey dariya dekha
@HujjatELC
On Ashura day we saw that hope (Qasim) diminsh

Jiski hasrat leeye duniya sey gaye sabze qabasubah e ashoora ko loot tey huvey sehra dekha
@HujjatELC
we saw river’s desire to quench their thirst
